      "raw_text": "Fearing that the great weight Of snow will cause the\ncollapse Of the Monroe st. bridge Commissioner ONO this\nafternoon ordered the Washington Water Power Co. to\nstop running the structure The commissioner\nthen sent out men round up abores whom he has put\nto work with shovels cleaning the bridge.\n\n\nSaid Mr. ONO:\n\n\n1--WE cannot afford to take any chances with that\nstructure until expert examines it. It out of line and\nhorrible loss of life might result should it go down."
    }
